title: Check_MK site backup job state
agents: linux
catalog: app/check_mk
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check checks the status of Check_MK site backup jobs. It
 will raise a {CRIT} state in case the job failed or the next execution of
 the job is overdue.

item:
 The site_id joined with the ident of the job (string).

inventory:
 One service per site and backup job will be created.
